1. Authentication

Method	URL	Body	Description
POST	/api/auth/register	{ "username": "string", "email": "string", "password": "string", "display_name": "string (optional)", "is_admin": true/false (optional) }	Register a new user
POST	/api/auth/login	{ "username": "string", "password": "string" }	Login a user, returns session info
GET	/api/auth/session	None	Returns current logged-in user info
DELETE	/api/auth/logout	None	Logout user

2. Users
Method	URL	Body	Description
PATCH	/api/users/:userId	{ "username": "string (optional)", "email": "string (optional)", "display_name": "string (optional)" }	Update a user's profile (admin or self)
DELETE	/api/users/:userId	None	Delete a user (admin or self)

3. Forums

Method	URL	Body	Description
GET	/api/forums	None	List all public, unblocked forums
GET	/api/forums/:forumId	None	Get forum details
POST	/api/forums	{ "title": "string", "description": "string (optional)" }	Create a forum (requires login)
DELETE	/api/forums/:forumId	None	Delete a forum (admin only)
PATCH	/api/forums/:forumId/block	{ "blocked": true/false }	Block/unblock forum (admin only)

4. Threads

Method	URL	Body	Description
GET	/api/forums/:forumId/threads	None	List threads in a forum (public + accessible private)
POST	/api/forums/:forumId/threads	{ "title": "string", "is_private": true/false (optional) }	Create a thread (login required)
GET	/api/threads/:threadId	None	Get thread details including moderators
PATCH	/api/threads/:threadId	{ "title": "string (optional)", "is_private": true/false (optional)" }	Update thread (owner only)
DELETE	/api/threads/:threadId	None	Delete thread (owner only)
PATCH	/api/threads/:threadId/block	{ "blocked": true/false }	Block/unblock thread (moderator only)

Thread Ownership & Moderators

Method	URL	Body	Description
POST	/api/threads/:threadId/owner	{ "newOwnerId": number }	Transfer ownership (current owner only)
POST	/api/threads/:threadId/moderators	{ "userId": number }	Add a moderator (owner only)
DELETE	/api/threads/:threadId/moderators/:userId	None	Remove a moderator (owner only)
Private Thread Members
Method	URL	Body	Description
POST	/api/threads/:threadId/members	{ "userId": number }	Invite member (moderator only)
DELETE	/api/threads/:threadId/members/:userId	None	Remove member (moderator only)
GET	/api/threads/:threadId/members	None	Get list of owner, moderators, members

5. Posts

Method	URL	Body	Description
GET	/api/threads/:threadId/posts	None	List posts in thread (unblocked only)
POST	/api/threads/:threadId/posts	{ "content": "string" }	Create a post (thread access required)
GET	/api/posts/:postId	None	Get a single post (unblocked only)
PATCH	/api/posts/:postId	{ "content": "string" }	Edit post (owner/admin only)
DELETE	/api/posts/:postId	None	Delete post (author/moderator/owner/admin)
PATCH	/api/posts/:postId/block	{ "blocked": true/false }	Block/unblock post (moderator/owner/admin)

6. Admin

Method	URL	Body	Description
GET	/api/administrator/users	None	List all users with roles
PATCH	/api/administrator/users/:userId/block	{ "blocked": true/false }	Block/unblock a user
PATCH	/api/administrator/users/:userId/role	{ "roleId": number }	Update user's role
GET	/api/admin/threads	None	List all threads
GET	/api/admin/posts	None	List all posts
GET	/api/admin/blocked	None	List blocked users, forums, threads, posts

7. Setup

Method	URL	Body	Description
POST	/api/setup/make-admin	{ "username": "string" }	Make a user admin (for initial setup)